articles.title: Erin Franke
articles.description: Hi, I'm Erin Franke. I am currently a student at Macalester College double majoring in Applied Mathemetics & Statistics and Economics with a passion for data analysis in sports and social good among other fields.
articles.contents:
In addition to my academics, some things I enjoy are playing softball at Macalester, volunteering at my local food pantry in Chicago, getting out into nature, and watching baseball (especially the Cubs).
